list.abstract: 英语单词，基本释义为结婚典礼，做名词。

yingyinNormal.en: I'll see you at the wedding.
yingyinNormal.zh: 婚礼上见。

yingyinNormal.en: It was a beautiful wedding.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那是场美妙的婚礼。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, isn't it a gay wedding?
yingyinNormal.zh: 难道不是同志婚礼吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Who's ready for a wedding?
yingyinNormal.zh: 大家准备好参加婚礼了吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Ha ha, you have to go to a wedding.
yingyinNormal.zh: 嘿嘿，有人得去参加婚礼咯。

yingyinNormal.en: You can't play bagpipes at the wedding.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你不能在婚礼上吹风笛。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, they're not in the wedding.
yingyinNormal.zh: 哦, 那个, 他们不会出现在婚礼仪式上。

yingyinNormal.en: This is not a gay wedding. Wasting time talking.
yingyinNormal.zh: 别再提同志婚礼了。别废话了。

yingyinNormal.en: You gotta take it now. No, this your wedding.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你可以现在验。不，这是你的婚礼。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, I did. But then that wedding never happened.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我写过，但那个婚礼没有如期而至。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, you're going to a wedding alone? That's sad.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你要形单影只的去参加婚礼吗？好惨呐。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, have you and Howard started planning your wedding yet?
yingyinNormal.zh: 嗨，你和霍华德开始计划婚礼了吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Chandler. He's your father; he should be at the wedding.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他是你爸爸，他应该来参加我们的婚礼。

yingyinNormal.en: Mrs Hughes, doesn't Carson deserve a wedding in this house?
yingyinNormal.zh: 休斯太太，卡森难道不该在这里办婚礼吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Keep the change. And buy your dad-husband a wedding gift.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不用找了，就当是送你老爸老公的结婚礼吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Wait. I want to have a first dance with you. Right here? At our wedding. This is our wedding. No. I want a real wedding.
yingyinNormal.zh: 等等。我想和你跳婚礼上的第一支舞。就在这儿吗？在我们的婚礼上。这就是我们的婚礼呀。不。我想要一场真的婚礼。

yingyinNormal.en: And you need a little help here, so is a gay wedding shorter or longer than a straight wedding?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我来帮你一把，同志婚礼跟普通婚礼比是长点还是短点？

yingyinNormal.en: I'm thinking double wedding.
yingyinNormal.zh: 双重婚礼有戏了。

yingyinNormal.en: The wedding. There's going to be a wedding. Young lady, don't you sit there and tell me my first grandchild is going to be a bastard.
yingyinNormal.zh: 婚礼，你们得举行婚礼，小姑娘，你休想坐在那里告诉我，我的第一个外孙会是个私生子。

yingyinNormal.en: That's true. Yeah. Poppy. Oh, I'm gonna be a poppy. So when is the wedding? Who?
yingyinNormal.zh: 没错，我要当外公了，我要当外公了，婚礼什么时候举行？谁的婚礼？
